Uhawe ikaze kuri Ministry Assistant – porogaramu izagufasha kumenya uko ubwiriza mu buryo bworoshye cyane!

Ministry Assistant ituma ubasha kwandika ifasi nshya wahawe mu buryo bworoshye kandi bwihuse, gukurikiranira hafi abo usubira gusura na raporo yawe ya buri kwezi, kandi ugapanga uko uri bubwirize uwo munsi.
"Ushobora guhita wandika izina ry'umuhanda, inyubako y'amagorofa cyangwa ifasi iri mu cyaro, guhitamo ibintu bituriye ifasi yawe, ndetse rwose ukaba wanafata ifoto y' ikarita y'ifasi."

"Andika izina ry'umuhanda ndetse na nomero nini iri ku muhanda hamwe na nomero nto kurusha iyindi kuri uwo muhanda kugira ngo izindi nomero zisigaye hagati zihite zikora. Urugero, “Umuhanda wajye, 1 kugeza 51, imibare y'ibiharwe”, haravuka imihanda yitwa 1, 3, 5, gutyo gutyo. Nanone ushobora gukoresha inyuguti niba zikoreshwa mu mazina y'imihanda, urugero: 1A, 1B, 1C, gutyo gutyo."

"Ibanga: Nomero nshya z'imihanda uzajya wongera ku zisanzwe zizajya zihita ziyongera ku zisanzwe zinitondeke ku buryo zigira urutonde rwiza . Ibyo ni ko bizagenda niwongeramo amagorofa mashya cyangwa inyito nshya wise inzu usanze mu bipangu."
"Aha uba ushobora guhitamo umubare w'amagorofa ari muri iyo nyubako ndetse ukanandika amazina y'ababa kuri buri gorofa."

"Ibanga: Nushyira izina ry'umuhanda na nomero y'igorofa icyarimwe mu hagenewe gushyirwamo izina ry'umuhanda, iyi porogaramu izajya ihita iguhishurira icyarimwe ubwinjiro n'aho bazamukira mu muturirwa. Ibyo bizagufasha gutembera mu ifasi yawe mu buryo bworoshye igihe wagiye kubwiriza."
"Jya wongera ubusobanuro kuri buri aderesi. Mu buryo butandukanye n'imiturirwa n'aderesi z'imihanda, aderesi zo mu cyaro ntizizajya zitondeka ku murongo, zizajya zikurikirana nk'uko wazishyizemo."
Ibanga: Ushobora kujya uzitondekanya mu buryo ushaka kandi biroroshye hakurikijwe icyo ushaka kugenderaho utondeka.

"Biroroshye kwandika umusaruro w'ibyo ubona igihe uri kubwiriza mu ifasi yawe, wenda se niba nyir'inzu atagaragaje ugushimishwa cyangwa nta gihe yari afite, cyangwa se wenda niba wasize ibaruwa mu gasanduku k'ibaruwa (niba byemewe iwanyu) byatewe n'uko utabahasanze, cyangwa ukandika izina ry'umuntu mushya usanze mu rugo wagezeho mbere."
"Ibanga: Ushobora kujya wandika aderesi nshya z'agace ugezemo igihe cyose uri kubwiriza mu ifasi yawe."

"Ushobora kujya ureba umubare w'ingo utarasura, umubare w'abashimishijwe mu ifasi, n'ibindi, ndetse ushobora guhita utahura urutonde rw'aderesi ziri ku muhanda wanditse, aderesi z'abo utarasura, cyangwa aderesi z'abashimishijwe. Ushobora no kubona ibarurishamibare ry'iminsi wakoze mu ifasi yawe ndetse n'amasaha wagiye uyikoramo mbere."

"Igihe ubonye umuntu ushimishijwe, uge wandika ibintu runaka bigaragaza ko wamusuye. Ushobora kwandika izina rye n'izina ry'undi muntu mu muryango w'abo wahasanze, indimi bakoresha, aderesi ya interineti, n'andi makuru yose yagufasha."

"Ibanga: Biroroshye ko wakwikorera urutonde rw'ibitabo ukabiha impinamagambo zawe bwite, cyangwa se niba ubishaka ukandika icyo igitabo cyangwa igazeti wasigiye umuntu bivugaho muri make, aho kwandika ukwezi yasohokeye."
"Igihe usubiye gusura umuntu, wowe uzajya ukanda ahagenewe kwandika ikiganiro hafi y'izina rye hanyuma wandike muri make ibyo mwaganiriye."

"Abantu bashimishijwe mwahuye uri mu ifasi biroroshye guhita ubongera ku rutonde rw'abo uzajya usura. Nanone ushobora kujya wandika gusubira gusura ku bantu mwahuye ariko batabarizwa mu ifasi yawe bwite."

Abo wasubiye gusura bashobora gutondekwa hakurikijwe aho baherereye, iminsi ishize utabasura, cyangwa ugahera ku bo wikundiye uzajya uhita ureba hafi muri ino porogaramu kugira ngo urusheho kubitaho mu buryo bwihariye.

"Koresha uburyo bwo kugaragaza abo wikundiye kugira ngo umenye abo kwitaho cyane, urugero niba ushaka gupanga abo ugomba gusura uwo munsi nubundi cyangwa muri icyo cyumweru. Kimwe n'uko utondeka abo usubira gusura, nanone abo wikundiye, wabatondeka ushingiye ku ho batuye cyangwa ku gihe hashize utabasura."

"Kugira ngo umenye uko ukora umurimo wo kubwiriza, uzajya wandika raporo y'ibyo umaze iminsi ukora unarebe niba uri kugira amajyambere mu murimo muri uko kwezi cyangwa se ahubwo mu mwaka w'umurimo wose."
"Ushobora nanone guhitamo icyiciro cy'umubwiriza ubarizwamo, wenda se niba uri umupayiniya w'umufasha, cyangwa se unishyirireho intego ugomba kugeraho muri uko kwezi mu murimo wo kubwiriza."
"Ukwezi nikurangira, Ministry Assistant izagufasha gutegura raporo yawe ndetse inagufashe kuyohereza umwanditsi w'itorero."

"Ibanga: Ushobora kubanza kwandika nomero ya telefoni cyangwa aderesi ya interineti uzajya woherezaho raporo. Aho uzabyandika uzahasanga kuri meni y'igenamiterere, kugira ngo ntuzage uhora uyandukura igihe cyose ugiye kohereza raporo."

"Ni ngombwa ko uzajya utegeka ino porogaramu ikagukorera buri gihe kopi y'amakuru ifite ikayabika mu gafayili gato ibika ku cyuma cyawe, hato utazatakaza raporo y'uko wabwirije mu ifasi cyangwa abo wasubiye gusura kuko icyuma cyawe gishobora gupfa isaha n'isaha, kwibwa, cyangwa se hakabaho n'ikindi kintu utari witeze."

"Inama: Ushobora kubona twa meni duto tw'aho ugeze uri gukoresha ino porogaramu, binyuriye mu gukanda ukagumishaho ku kintu ubonye."
